WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.350
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:05.997 --> 00:00:08.580
ALAN SEALES: "In Transit" is a
funny and poignant new Broadway

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:11.250
musical which follows the
intertwined lives of 11 New

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:13.560
Yorkers faced with the
challenges of city life

00:00:13.560 --> 00:00:15.920
with a groundbreaking
a capella score

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:17.670
by a team including
the creators of "Pitch

00:00:17.670 --> 00:00:18.720
Perfect" and "Frozen."

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:20.970
"In Transit" takes you on a
journey with people hoping

00:00:20.970 --> 00:00:23.340
to catch the express
train to their dreams,

00:00:23.340 --> 00:00:25.530
including the stops
they make along the way.

00:00:25.530 --> 00:00:27.540
Modern yet timeless,
"In Transit"

00:00:27.540 --> 00:00:29.460
is a story about all
of us, set to music

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:32.280
that will stay with you
long after the ride is over.

00:00:32.280 --> 00:00:34.787
Please welcome to the stage
the cast of "In Transit."

